snippet.title: Girl Zone (Last Minute Cleaning)
snippet.description:
Apparently we're meant to pick up the most vital items. According to this game, that's not survival items, but fashion items!

Broadcasted live on Twitch -- Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/the_gaming_archaeologist

#letspuzzle #cringe #sexist
